  <name>Standard Notes</name>
  <summary>A simple and private place for your notes, thoughts, and life's work</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Standard Notes is free to use on every platform, and comes standard with cross-platform sync and end-to-end
      privacy. Your notes are encrypted and secured so only you can decrypt them. No one but you can read your notes
      (not even us).
    </p>
    <p>
      For those wanting a little more power and flexibility, we created Extended, which unlocks powerful editors,
      themes, and automated backups.
    </p>
